data.description: Introducing this beautiful residential property that combines comfort, style, and functionality. This 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home provides ample space for families or individuals seeking room to grow. It also offers a generous layout with an open concept. The kitchen features sleek stainless steel appliances that not only elevate the space aesthetically but also offer modern conveniences and durability. The master suite boasts a garden tub, separate shower, dual vanity and walk in closet. The remaining bedrooms are versatile, providing options for play rooms, guest rooms, or home office space. Located in the Creekside Hills subdivision, this community offers an in-ground pool, playground and much more. Schedule a showing today!
